data.description:
Excellent and beautifully maintained 3bd/2ba ranch home in Callaway Village, a Swim/Tennis Community! Conveniently located just minutes from McDonough Square, Shopping, Restaurants and I-75, this home features: split bedroom plan, formal dining room, tiled floors in kitchen and bathrooms, spacious living room with fireplace, generous sized master bedroom with a walk-in closet an en-suite bathroom with a garden tub and separate shower, nice sized secondary bedrooms and an additional bathroom, 2 car garage and a large fenced-in backyard with a storage shed.
